## Critical Pre-Requisites (Do These First)

Before ANY submission, you need these three things done:

1. **Tool safety annotations on all 3 tools** — Without this, every Anthropic submission gets auto-rejected
2. **Privacy policy at `https://suprawall.ai/privacy`** — Required by both Anthropic directories AND good practice for LangChain/Vercel
3. **Remove `node_modules` from git** — Signals amateur repo management to reviewers

These three fixes take under 2 hours and unblock everything else.